OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain dry through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with variable cloud. There
OL,8,Fwill be some sunny then clear spells.
OL,9,FWinds will fall mostly light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FIt will be cool with variable
OL,12,Fcloud and some bright or sunny spells
OL,13,Fat times. Showers pushing south later
OL,14,Fin the day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FEarly
OL,17,Frain on Monday followed by bright
OL,18,Fspells and showers, these continuing
OL,19,Fthrough Tuesday and Wednesday, and
OL,20,Fbecoming heavy and blustery at times.
OL,21,FRemaining cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
